data.description: Welcome to this charming, recently updated home in award winning Owen J Roberts School District.  With five bedrooms  and two family rooms this home offers tons of space!  A recently updated and opened floor plan,  with brand new central air.  The lighting in this home is amazing, enjoy the gorgeous sunrises from the rear deck and patio of the home.  The home has spacious bedrooms with a primary bedroom that leads out onto a private deck.  Outside there is a nice level yard with paver patio to enjoy the outdoor space.  Two car garage attached to the home with ample parking in the driveway.
